<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-3341] Improve error handling on invalid requests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3341</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should include the request id in the error message if parsing of `RequestHeader` fails and we should not try to mute the selector after closing the connection due to an error (as it causes a second exception to be thrown).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12947586">KAFKA-3341</key>
            <summary>Improve error handling on invalid requests</summary>
